messages.text: Yeah. Miss u like crazy u know.
idk, my Mom hid them from me.
I’m in her rm atm looking 4 them.
She’s been pacing n the kitchen since my bro left.
idk. She asked him 2 go buy something & bring it back.
Did she try 2 call the cops again?
They said they can’t do anything.
Basically, they’ll only come if 1 of us shows up dead 1st.
I’ve never seen her like this.
Get her 2 pack up the car & come back here.
She won’t leave. We can’t afford it.
U guys could stay at our house.
"Dear Watkins Family - This house is mine, so you know. But I enjoy the fresh young blood you’ve brought to me. Tell her not to take any candy from strangers."
"Dear Watkins Family -  Please know that I’m taking note of who is in the bedrooms that face the street. It helps me to know who is in which, so I can plan better."
U have 2 get out of there.
I’ve been hearing noises at night.
And last night, I had a dream a man was standing over my bed.
What if it wasn’t a dream?!
I feel like I’m going to throw up.
Listen, there’s nothing 2 b afraid of.
u just said I needed to get out of here!
I know, but thinking more, this guy is prbbly just lonely.
Well, u miss me, & u don’t write these kinds of letters 2 the people across the street do u?
I might have written those letters to u.
I was kind of hoping u guys might move back here.
Ure a sick asshole, u know that?
Maisey, I’m sorry. Plz don’t h8 me.
I saw this news article where this hppnd in NJ.
"If you want a clue what you’re in for if you stay here, see what I’ve stored in the master bedroom’s wall. Your blood will be dripping inside my mouth by midnight."
What kind of sick freak writes sthing like that!?
Oh yeah sure. I’m telling my Mom.
Not picking up. And my bro just got back with a sledgehammer.
He and my Mom told me 2 go 2 my room.
Now I’m going 2 let them tear dwn the wall and charge u 4 it.
Maisey, just stay tlking w me until they r done ok?
Ure lucky I’m tlking  2 u at all.
Maisey, I swear on ur Dad’s grave, I ddn’t write that last letter.
They r mking so much noise.
This is all ur effing fault
Just stay in ur room, okay?
I think someone else is in there.
she stopped screaming, & I just hrd smthing slam against the wall.
I hear footsteps that don’t sound like his
No. I don’t want them 2 hear my phone.
What if they hear me talkng on the phone?
I’ll call from the landline here.
I have them on the phone.
sweat on my hands is mking it hard 2 txt
The dispatcher says 2 stay where u r.
I’m keeping them on the line 2 keep them updated.
39.988900, -74.182499 - do u know what that is?
It’s the exact coordinates of where we 1st kissed on the swing @ Castle Park when we were 12.
We left school, & tried 2 race each other atw home, but u tripped & hurt ur ankle.
So I put u on the swing, til ur folks cld come get u.
And while we were waiting, that’s when I decided 2 do it.
When all this is over, I’ll use my allowance to fly u back 2 that spot.
Ur freaking me out! What’s happening??
Maisey, I thought sthing hppened 2 u.
Did the cops get there yet?
Tell me when they do, ok?
